\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Mrs. Sabita Saha joined Aditya Group in 1994 as a teacher at Aditya Academy, R.D.C Road Dumdum. From the very first day of her association with the group, she has been an epitome of integrity and trust.\n\nShe has a constructive approach to work and steadfastly pushes self and others for results. She has actively involved herself with the administration and academic enhancement of students in all the Aditya Group of Schools with her exemplary functional skills. She fosters a climate of inclusion where diverse thoughts are freely shared and integrated. She uses her vast experience and analytical skills to solve difficult problems with effective solutio<\/h6>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>About Us Aditya Academy Secondary, Dumdum One of the prime CBSE affiliated schools in Kolkata, Aditya Academy Senior Secondary is a part of the Aditya group founded by Mr Bhaskar Aditya. The school has been regarded as one of the best CBSE English Medium schools in Kolkata. Aditya Group is a business house established in &hellip;<\/p>\n<p class=\"read-more\"> <a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/aditya-academy-secondary-b34262.ingress-bonde.ewp.live\/about\/\"> <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">About<\/span> Read More &raquo;<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"page-builder","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"disabled","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"disabled","ast-featur